--[[
    Advanced Auto Farm V17 (Modifiers & Smart DMG Scaling)
    Final Logic Overhaul:
    - Pre-Farm Scan: Script now scans ALL matching NPCs and compares HP before TPing.
    - Targeting: Strictly picks the lowest HP target from the entire pool.
    - Attribute Support: Now checks 'BaseHealth' attribute (fixes 4.5e+22 issues).
    - Defense Skip: Instead of stopping, it now skips targets you can't damage.
    - Optimized Load: Reduced initial wait times for faster startup.
    - Search Bar Fix: Ensured search bar starts cleared.
    - Stability: Fixed 'Argument 1 missing or nil' in forceFire.
    - Logic Fix: Added strict "Is Tool Equipped" check to prevent farm-start before tool is ready.
]]

